ICO.Description:
JustDatingSite.com is a classical free dating site with premium services s with a fixed price in fiat currencies. These prices will vary for different countries/regions, and 100% of payments will be used to buy out Just Dating Coins (JDC). 

Team:

  • Roman Agafonov: Founder 
  • Anton Shashok: Social Researcher
  • Aleksei Morozov: COO

Just Dating Site will hold its ICO on the 15h of August, 2017. During the campaign, 70% of the tokens will be sold at a 1mBTC price each. The minimum target for the ICO is $200k with the cap being $3m. The ICO is expected to end on the 30th of September, 2017.

Token Reserve Split (30%):

  • 15% JDC were sold by the price 0.25 mBts / 1 JDC.
  • 15% JDC will be distributed among key partners and bounty program.
